ortance that SEO has these days. When you consider that the vast majority of people searching for things online will never make it past the first page of search results, the ability to get yourself in the top ten results is more important than ever before. Your ability to get there [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/what-are-the-most-effective-types-of-wordpress-content-for-raising-your-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Nora Mork\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6644:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/what-are-the-most-effective-types-of-wordpress-content-for-raising-your-seo/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/content-tips-e1553263352821.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"What Are the Most Effective Types of WordPress Content for Raising Your SEO?\" alt=\"What Are the Most Effective Types of WordPress Content for Raising Your SEO?\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>There’s no denying the\nimportance that SEO has these days. When you consider that the vast\nmajority of people searching for things online will never make it\npast the first page of search results, the ability to get yourself in\nthe top ten results is more important than ever before.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your ability to get there\ndoes, of course, depend on getting you SEO processes and techniques,\nwhich of course comes from your content and the types of content\nyou’re using. Nevertheless, if you’re trying to boost your SEO\nranking, can you just post anything, or is there a particular type of\ncontent you should be posting? \n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Today, we’re going to\nfind out.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Posts Leading the\nIndustry</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>When people are searching\nfor content in any niche or industry, it goes without saying that\nthey’re looking for the websites and people that hold the most\nauthority in what they say. Consider what sort of topics you’re\ninto. \n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you go for small blogs\nthat nobody has heard of, or do you go for the well-known and\nreliable publications? The chances are you go for the latter, so your\njob as a website or company is to become the authority in your niche.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Talk About Trending\nSubjects</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s always going to\nbe content that’s trending. This is content that’s currently\npopular in an industry or niche, and everyone is talking about it. In\norder to boost your SEO, you want to be talking about content that\nfits this trending category in order for more people to come to your\nwebsite.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hand in hand with the\nconsideration above, talking about relevant, trending topics will not\nonly boost the SEO ranking of your website, but it will also help\nmore people discover you easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>High-Quality, Accurate\nContent</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s so important to\nmake sure your content, no matter what content you’re posting, is\nhighly accurate and oozes quality. If your content is full of\nmistakes and typos, your readers are simply going to bounce, and this\nwill harm your SEO ranking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even if you’re not a\nprofessional writer, here are some professional online tools that can\nhelp you obtain quality content;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://viawriting.com/\">Via Writing</a> / <a href=\"https://academadvisor.com/\">Academ advisor</a> &#8211; Use these two services to make sure you’re using grammar properly in your online content. </li><li><a href=\"https://bigassignments.com/assignment-writing-services/assignment-help-perth\">Big Assignments</a> / <a href=\"https://oxessays.com/pay-for-essay\">Ox Essays</a> &#8211; These are two online proofreading services, as recommended by <a href=\"https://bestaustralianwriters.com/\">Bestaustralianwriters</a> to make sure your content is free from errors. </li><li><a href=\"https://studydemic.com/top-essay-writing-services/\">Study demic</a> / <a href=\"https://stateofwriting.com/\">State of Writing</a> &#8211; These are two blogs full of tips and advice on how to help you write SEO-optimised content. </li><li><a href=\"https://paperfellows.com/coursework-help\">Paper Fellows</a> / <a href=\"https://australianhelp.com/\">Australian Help</a> &#8211; As reviewed by <a href=\"https://ukservicesreviews.com/\">Ukservicesreviews</a>, these are two services to help you edit and perfect your online content. </li><li><a href=\"https://mywritingway.com/\">My Writing Way</a> / <a href=\"https://simplegrad.com/best-essay-writing-services/\">Simple Grad</a> &#8211; These are two websites full of online writing guides to help you master the art of SEO writing. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Use Visuals</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s true that a\npicture can speak a thousand words, and this is especially true on\nthe internet. When creating content, try to make it as visual as\npossible to make it more engaging, and therefore, a lot more\neffective.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At a basic level, this\nmeans including images and photos in your content, but if you want to\ntake things to the next level, use video content or produce\ninfographics to help spread your message.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Detailed How-To Guides</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the biggest\nconsiderations to think about when it comes to high-ranking SEO pages\nis the bounce rate. This is the time it takes from the moment people\nclick onto your website page to the time it takes for them to click\noff.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“A small bounce rate, which means someone clicking onto your page and clicking off again in no time at all, is bad for SEO because it says to Google, you’re not giving people the content they were looking for or intended you to have,” shares Ben Turner, an SEO expert for <a href=\"https://academized.com/\">Academized</a> and <a href=\"https://eliteassignmenthelp.com/university-assignments\">Eliteassignmenthelp</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is why How-To\ncontent is a great way to boost your SEO because people will stay on\nthe page for much longer because they’re following exactly how to\ndo what you’re telling them to do. The longer your bounce rate, the\nbetter your SEO will be.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>A Good, Old Listicle</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s no denying the\nimpact that listicle content has had on the internet; people\nabsolutely love them. This is because they’re very customizable to\nsuit whatever message you’re trying to send, and the information is\norganized in an easily consumable way.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Get creative with your\nlists and aim to create really engaging headlines that draw people in\nbefore literally bullet-pointing answers that people can retrieve\nreal value from.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/what-are-the-most-effective-types-of-wordpress-content-for-raising-your-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:106:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/what-are-the-most-effective-types-of-wordpress-content-for-raising-your-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"Top Best WordPress Plugins to Have On Your Site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 10:01:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Introducing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://oceanwp.org/?p=389203\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1269:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/wordpress-923188_1280-1-e1553154809517.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"Top Best WordPress Plugins to Have On Your Site\" alt=\"Top Best WordPress Plugins to Have On Your Site\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">WordPress is one of the best platforms for content creators. It is easy to use and it provides those with amazing content to share an avenue for broadcasting their thoughts and ideas to the world. You don’t need any programming skills to use WordPress and this is another reason why the platform is popular with [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sonia Bell\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8514:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/wordpress-923188_1280-1-e1553154809517.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"Top Best WordPress Plugins to Have On Your Site\" alt=\"Top Best WordPress Plugins to Have On Your Site\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>WordPress is one of the best platforms for content creators. It is easy to use and it provides those with amazing content to share an avenue for broadcasting their thoughts and ideas to the world. You don’t need any programming skills to use WordPress and this is another reason why the platform is <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/24-must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/\">popular with content creators</a>. To gain immensely from WordPress, users are advised to add WordPress plugins so as to extend the platform’s functionality. In this article, we will highlight some of the must-have WordPress plugins that will help your site soar to amazing heights. </p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Everest Forms</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Everest Forms is an advanced contact form plugin that allows site visitors to contact website administrators. When you post content on your website, the visitors to your site may want to leave feedback and this contact form is ideal for this purpose. Feedback from your site visitors will help you make necessary adjustments that will enhance the online experience and Everest Forms is the go-to contact form for modern websites. You can create beautiful contact forms for your online audience using the easy to use plug and play interface. This plugin offers 2 design options which are Default and Classic. You can use the plugin to create complex forms with advanced fields such as drop-down menu, checkboxes and radio buttons or you can opt for simple forms. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Unlimited forms. </li><li>Supports multiple layouts. </li><li>Drag and drop fields. </li><li>Multiple email recipients. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing plan: FREE</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>MonsterInsights</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>MonsterInsights works with Google Analytics to analyze the traffic to your website. Learning about the visitors to your site is one of the things that you need to do if you want to <a href=\"https://themegrill.com/blog/best-wordpress-plugins/\">improve your website’s performance</a> and this is the right tool for that purpose. MonsterInsight allows you to understand things such as where the visitors to your website are coming from and the sections on your website that are popular with visitors. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Simple setup. </li><li>Real-time stats</li><li>Universal tracking. </li><li>Popular post tracking. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing plan: FREE</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>SearchIQ</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Finding information on your website should not be difficult and that is why you need a tool that will help the visitors find what they want. SearchIQ was developed for this specific purpose and it is able to deliver fast and accurate <a href=\"https://websitesetup.org/best-popular-wordpress-plugins/\">searches on your website</a>. With this WordPress plugin, you can access statistics for the key phrases that users search in your website and this will help you re-think and adjust your content strategy so as to grow your website. This one is the best choice for health sites that contain much <a href=\"https://potencyup.com/\">info about medical issues</a> or pills.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Easy to set up. </li><li>Customizable user interface. </li><li>AI handles typos, fuzzy matches and synonyms.</li><li>Results optimized for relevant content. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Price plan: FREE</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Jetpack</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Jetpack is a comprehensive toolkit for WordPress that allows website owners to design, secure, and grow their <a href=\"https://athemes.com/collections/best-wordpress-plugins/\">websites from one bundle</a>. Jetpack WordPress plugin allows users to customize their websites with rich content such as themes and images. It also allows users to customize how their website content is shared on their social media platforms. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Powerful and intuitive customization tools. </li><li>Lots of professional themes. </li><li>Integration with WordPress mobile apps. </li><li>Lazy image loading. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Price plans: FREE. </p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>CSS &amp; JavaScript Toolbox</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>CSS &amp; JavaScript Toolbox is a WordPress plugin that allows users to improve the appearance and functionality of their websites. Users can use the toolkit to manage and inject JS, CSS, HTML and PHP code for effective website performance. Users can create and test scripts on one dashboard before launching. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Distraction-free editing</li><li>Code auto-completion. </li><li>Auto-backup for code blocks. </li><li>Powerful editing environment. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Price plan: CSS JS Toolbox PLUS – Free edition</p>\n\n\n\n<p> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;CSS JS Toolbox PLUS Support &#8211; $59</p>\n\n\n\n<p> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;CSS JS Toolbox PLUS Forever &#8211; $199</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>WP Rocket</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Online visitors expect the websites they visit to load up fast and when this doesn’t happen, they abandon that page immediately. As a website owner, this is the last thing you want to happen and WP Rocket is one of the for best WordPress plugins for website optimization. WP Rocket is a caching plugin for WordPress. It allows website owners and administrators to improve the speed of their WordPress sites instantly and to boost the performance even when they have no technical skills. This plugin turns on cache settings to allow DNS pre-fetching, lazy image loading, CDN support so as to improve the load times for web pages. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Page caching</li><li>Simple and easy to set up. </li><li>Cache preloading</li><li>Static files compression. </li><li>Images on request. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Price plan: Single &#8211; $49 (1 year support for 1 website), Plus &#8211; $99 (1 year support for 3 websites), Infinite &#8211; $249 (1 year for unlimited websites). </p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Yoast SEO</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite the fact that it is on the 7<sup>th</sup> place, this plugin is essential for everyone who is serious about SEO. The content on your website should be optimized for search engines so as to increase its ranking. This key plugin shows all possible issues you have and how to fix it. Even housewives who <a href=\"https://mommystips.com/mothers-entrepreneurs-make-money-from-home/\">decide to earn money from home</a> can easily handle website optimization with Yoast SEO. It will help you increase the traffic to your website by guiding your content development strategy. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Keyword optimization. </li><li>Page preview. </li><li>Readability check. </li><li>No duplicate content. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Price plan: Free, Premium &#8211; $89</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To make the most of your WordPress website, you will need to leverage the power of plugins and this article highlights some of the best plugins for modern websites. These plugins improve the performance of websites and make it easy for others to locate and use the website. Anyone with a website should, therefore, find useful plugins for their website and this article will provide you with all the information that you need to know about some of these plugins. &nbsp;<br></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/top-best-wordpress-plugins-to-have-on-your-site/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0