n a short while. The social media got deserved attention and exposure for all the right reasons. Today, most businesses have an Instagram page for their company to reach out to a wide audience. The platform boasts of more than 400 [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Walter Moore\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4684:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/wordpress-instagram-plugin.png\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" title=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" alt=\"Easy Tips to Include Instagram in Web Design Using WordPress\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Instagram is a cool, informal picture-sharing platform and has taken the world by storm in a short while. The social media got deserved attention and exposure for all the right reasons. Today, most businesses have an Instagram page for their company to reach out to a wide audience. The platform boasts of more than 400 million users. And it is no wonder why the top brands are latching on to this photo-sharing site for the success of their business. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many companies today use the Instagram\nStories feature to make their business presence felt. Then, why should web\ndesign be an exception? According to an article published on <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/322742\">https://www.entrepreneur.com</a>, your business should be a part of\nInstagram for numerous reasons. One is 20 percent of stories posted by brands,\nleveraging the platform, lead to direct interaction with a prospective\ncustomer. Therefore, read on to learn about some of the tips to include\nInstagram in web design via WordPress. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Embed\nfeeds </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to incorporate Instagram into\nyour website design is by embedding the feeds. You may have an Instagram theme\nthat would gel well with your website colors, graphics, logos, and existing\nproducts. Make the most out of the platform to make the integration unified. You\ncan embed your Instagram content through a plug-in. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to experts in the industry, a\nplug-in comes with enhanced functionalities. Let us explain this point with the\nhelp of an example. You can add your images to the website gallery and\nintegrate a slider. The plug-in will let you backup your Instagram images and\nvideos to your website. Additionally, you can display these together with\ncustomized taxonomies. Moreover, when the users like your photos and videos, it\nwill help you gain more <a href=\"https://instamacro.com/\">Instagram\nfollowers</a>\nin the process. Besides, you can gain control of imported posts that will\nundergo formatting for getting custom post types and post formats. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Include\nInstagram badge </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Opt for the integrations that work best\nfor your web design. If your website has a flawless design with flying graphics\nor animations, for example, there is nothing like it. The inclusion of the Instagram\nlogo with other social media logos at the bottom of the left-hand corner of your\nsite is extremely important. The dark base highlights the white color without\ndistracting users from your website’s unique design and high-resolution images.\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Include\na page with sales in focus</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can design a web page with sales in\nfocus. When companies such as White Fox Boutique can create a page with sales\nintent, why not you? Moreover, Instagram has started to include e-businesses\ninto it via its latest initiative Instagram for business. Then, advertising\ncosts are very high and can go up to $350,000 to $1 million per month. If you\nhave supernormal profits, you can afford such expenses. On the contrary, if you\nown a startup or small business, such advertising expenses are not within your\nmeans. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make the most out of Instagram to\nintegrate into your web design. Therefore, as a designer, look for innovative\nways to enhance your web pages design and its reach to the global audience. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Author Bio:</strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Walter Moore is a notable management consultant and digital\nmarketing expert. He has helped e-commerce businesses in all niches gain <a href=\"https://instamacro.com/\">Instagram\nfollowers</a> with his effective marketing\nstrategies and guidance.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/easy-tips-to-include-instagram-in-web-design-using-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:1