t-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"premmerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16812:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/oceanwp_banner_2.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" title=\"How to boost your WooCommerce store results with OceanWP and Premmerce?\" alt=\"How to boost your WooCommerce store results with OceanWP and Premmerce?\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Are you sure you’re making the most of your OceanWP theme? Premmerce is here to demonstrate how to amplify your users’ navigation and products presentation and as a result sell more with the help of its plugins. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you got interested, read on and learn about features we developed and integrated into the OceanWP theme (which is one of the most popular themes in WordPress!). And, of course, we couldn&#8217;t but provide you with some real-life experience, so take your time and check out our OceanWP based <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">online store demo version here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Improving navigation features </h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Product Filter</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is a handy and flexible tool for managing filters for WooCommerce products. The main plugin features are a single widget that controls the display of all available filters and a well-designed caching system that improves the load speed, outperforming the standard WooCommerce filters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Advanced SEO settings for filters and the ability to control the filter URLs formation are available in the Premium version of the plugin. You can learn about all the plugins features <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-product-filter/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-1024x675.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380624\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-1024x675.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-300x198.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-768x506.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, you can view the OceanWP demo integrated with  Premmerce filters <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Variation Swatches</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce WooCommerce Variation Swatches will help you to visualize the product variations as well as enable your customers to buy a variational product from the product catalog.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-variation-swatches/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Display in the product archive:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-1024x657.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380723\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-1024x657.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-300x193.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-768x493.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2.png 1556w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Product variations are presented by colors and labels:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-1024x582.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380724\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-1024x582.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-300x171.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-768x437.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Product variations are presented by images:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-1024x563.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380725\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-1024x563.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-300x165.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-768x422.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with the Premmerce swatches set up  <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Product Search</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Search turns ‘product search’ into a live search and also provides additional search results using spell correction.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-product-search/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-1024x474.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380729\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-1024x474.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-300x139.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-768x356.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with set up Premmerce search <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Frequently Bought Together</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Frequently Bought Together will help you to create product sets that will increase sales through discounts in a bundle. This is one of the main marketing tools used by Amazon to raise the average check. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You  can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-frequently-bought-together/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-1024x608.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380746\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-1024x608.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-300x178.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6-768x456.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/6.png 1403w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Please view the OceanWP demo with Premmerce Frequently Bought Together <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/clothes/shirts/flowy-blouse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tools for usability improvement</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Wishlist</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>A wishlist is a tool that will allow your customers to choose and save products for future purchases and to share them with their friends. Just review wishlists and influence your customers’ by offering bargains and super deals based on the collected information.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-1024x581.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380753\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-1024x581.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-300x170.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/7-768x435.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce plugin addon &#8211; Premmerce Product Comparison</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Product comparison is a tool that will enable your customers to choose the best product, decide and make a purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-main-plugin-woocommerce-plugins-bundle/#reading-progress-title-4\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-1024x567.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380758\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-1024x567.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-300x166.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/8-768x425.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce WooCommerce Brands</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin allows you to create an unlimited number of brands that can be assigned to products for better cataloging, product search and additional opportunities for marketing and product promotion by brands.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-brands-free-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-1024x606.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380764\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-1024x606.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-300x178.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/9-1-768x455.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also view the OceanWP demo with set up Premmerce brands <a href=\"http://oceanwp.premmerce.com/brands/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Premmerce Woocommerce Multi-currency</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Premmerce Woocommerce Multi-currency plugin allows you to start a multi-currency store with flexible settings and a number of additional unique features.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-1024x531.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380765\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-1024x531.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-300x156.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/10-768x398.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To display the currency switcher in the top bar, just add the [multicurrency] shortcode to the Content field in the theme Customizer:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-1024x581.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381642\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-1024x581.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-300x170.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/13-768x436.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn about all the plugin features <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-multi-currency/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Optimizing performance &#8211; Premmerce Performance Optimizer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WooCommerce often doesn’t handle a number of performance issues encountered by the stores with a large product base without cache and third-party optimization. Thus, we’ve studied this problem, and as a result, we’ve designed the plugin that automatically optimizes your online store operations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, we’ve tested the performance of the OceanWP theme with 500k of products and the work of the Premmerce Performance Optimizer plugin. We’ve created the website where you can personally test and view all plugins in action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The test results are shown in the diagram:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Test 1 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce  plugins</li><li>Test 2 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce plugins + Premmerce Performance Optimizer</li><li>Test 3 &#8211; OceanWP + Premmerce plugins + Premmerce Performance Optimizer + WP Rocket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-1024x634.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-380781\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-1024x634.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-300x186.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12-768x475.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12.png 1380w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can read more about the test results and plugin features on this <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"page (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-performance-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\">page</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Additional plugins that don’t affect the store display</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also be interested in some  other Premmerce  plugins that will contribute to the flexible setup of your store:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce WooCommerce Permalink Manager (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-permalink-manager-remove-shop-product-product-category-url/\" target=\"_blank\">Premmerce WooCommerce Permalink Manager</a></strong> is developed to improve the current WooCommerce URL configuration features and provide your store with better display options and additional SEO capabilities to adhere to WooCommerce SEO Audit standards.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-redirect-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce Redirect Manager (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce Redirect Manager</a></strong> enables you to create 301 and 302 redirects and to set up the automatic redirects for the deleted products in the WooCommerce store.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce User Roles (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://premmerce.com/wordpress-custom-user-roles/\" target=\"_blank\">Premmerce User Roles</a></strong> &#8211;  this plugin has been developed for creating user roles from the WordPress admin area and assigning the arbitrary access rights to them. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-customers-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce WooCommerce Customers Manager (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce WooCommerce Customers Manager</a></strong> extends the standard user list and the edit user page in WordPress and adds the customer data from WooCommerce. This is the main customer management plugin from Premmerce, which we constantly improve by adding new features, considering the needs of its users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/premmerce-woocommerce-wholesale-pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Premmerce Woocommerce Wholesale Pricing (opens in a new tab)\">Premmerce Woocommerce Wholesale Pricing</a></strong> allows you to add prices to products for each user roles.     </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://premmerce.com/woocommerce-seo-addon-yoast/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WooCommerce SEO Addon (opens in a new tab)\">WooCommerce SEO Addon</a></strong> plugin extends the functionality of Yoast SEO for microdata management and provides all the instruments you need for your store’s SEO improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Premmerce plugins pricing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version is available in all Premmerce plugins and in many cases, it’s sufficient for dealing with a variety of issues. You can find all of them in the official <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/premmerce/#content-plugins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WordPress marketplace (opens in a new tab)\">WordPress marketplace</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some plugins offer Premium versions that complement and expand their basic capabilities. Also, the users of Premium versions get technical support and regular updates. Our team often add new features to the existing plugins, so your store is always trendy and functional as a result.  The price of Premium versions ranges from $ 45 to $ 65. Please, have a look at Premium versions in our marketplace.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Premmerce Suite</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to improve your OceanWP based online stores at once with all or most Premmerce plugins, we’ve prepared for you the <a href=\"https://premmerce.com/pricing/\">Premmerce Suite</a>, which provides the access to all the premium versions at a price just above the cost of 2 plugins.  Check it out!</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:101:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/how-to-boost-your-woocommerce-store-results-with-oceanwp-and-premmerce/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n							\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"7 Top Plugins to Turn a WordPress Site into a Mobile App\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 18:20:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Introducing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"https://oceanwp.org/?p=364764\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1307:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-to-mobileapp.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"7 Top Plugins to Turn a WordPress Site into a Mobile App\" alt=\"7 Top Plugins to Turn a WordPress Site into a Mobile App\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">Having a mobile app for your business has become inevitable if you want to be at the forefront of the competition. The reason is simple: a number of people are turning to their smartphones for almost everything &#8211; booking tickets, reading, shopping and much more. Earlier, mobile browsers or mobile websites were in the trend, [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Nirav Shastri\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12754:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-to-mobileapp.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"500\" title=\"7 Top Plugins to Turn a WordPress Site into a Mobile App\" alt=\"7 Top Plugins to Turn a WordPress Site into a Mobile App\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p>Having a mobile app for your business has become inevitable if you want to be at the forefront of the competition. The reason is simple: a number of people are turning to their smartphones for almost everything &#8211; booking tickets, reading, shopping and much more. Earlier, mobile browsers or mobile websites were in the trend, but today, it&#8217;s all about mobile apps. After all, they are convenient, fast and easy to use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, are you planning to build a mobile app but worried about incurring the cost of the same?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, we have an amazing solution to it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have already built a beautiful WordPress site, but not a mobile app, don&#8217;t worry. There&#8217;s always the much-in-trend DIY approach to opt for! Yes, even here!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a WordPress plugin, you can create a new and all-mobile channel to be available to your target audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are inquisitive to find more about how can a plugin assist in turning your WordPress site into a mobile app, take a look at the following!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Plugins that Can Convert a WordPress site into a mobile app</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the most popular plugins that can assist you in turning the WordPress site into a mobile app include:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/androapp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Androapp (opens in a new tab)\">Androapp</a> </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364813\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Opt for this plugin if you have a content-driven website like newspapers and blogs. This plugin takes your news feed and further turns it into a mobile-friendly layout. &nbsp;The outcome in the form of a mobile app will look similar to your responsive website. But, it obviously is more suitable than the website because of the presence of added functionalities like:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Image zooming</li><li>Saving content offline</li><li>Send unlimited push notifications</li><li>In-line ads</li><li>Support for WordPress/Facebook comments</li><li>Support for deep linking (if you want to highlight different pages of your app in the search)</li><li>Infinite scroll facility</li><li>Custom theme and colors to match with your website</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A quick note to follow here:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At least for time being, it is recommended to launch your app only on the Android platform as the functionality is currently in beta. But, building an iOS app can definitely be kept in your pipeline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/apppresser/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"AppPresser (opens in a new tab)\">AppPresser</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364814\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AppPresser is quite easy to use and has a dedicated WordPress mobile theme that further creates the mobile app for your WordPress site. &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you think that a free WordPress plugin won&#8217;t suffice your need and at the same time, don&#8217;t even want to pay for building the mobile app, this probably has to be your plugin choice. With it, you can get access to the following mobile app features:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WordPress plugin and extension compatibility (this means you can integrate features like Google maps, Facebook login, camera connectivity and so on)</li><li>Design navigation as tabs or pull-out menu</li><li>Custom page creation</li><li>Push notification</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Though it brands to be easy in nature, it is not considered to be an ideal tool for the non-developers. It requires extensive customization to build your app from scratch and actually make it work as an app. So, consider this plugin if you have a developer&#8217;s assistance at your side.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yournewsapp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Blappsta (opens in a new tab)\">Blappsta</a> </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364815\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Blappsta is completely free to use and is compatible with both Android and iOS platforms. It comes with a unique feature of &#8216;Blappsta Preview&#8217; which lets you test and preview your experiments before actually making it live. So, you can see how your site will look like in the mobile app form even before creating it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its features include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Facility of push notifications when a new post is live</li><li>Deep linking indexing for Google</li><li>Facility of share buttons of various social media platforms like Facebook and Twitter</li><li>Flexibility in organizing the content on your mobile app</li><li>Customize navigation as well as home page design</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you create the mobile app, it can display popular articles, support the videos; display your Facebook page and much more. However, it is still relatively a new plugin compared to others.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mobiloud-mobile-app-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"MobiLoud (opens in a new tab)\">MobiLoud</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364816\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Mobile App Canvas is a plugin created by MobiLoud which enables you to create a mobile app while launching it in both: Google Play Store and Apple App Store. It is one of the best plugin options to get a native mobile app from a WordPress site. You don&#8217;t need to create a separate theme, you can continue with your existing one for your app when you choose this plugin. Also, you have the flexibility of selecting a different theme altogether!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Features of MobiLoud include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Amazing range of themes for your mobile app</li><li>Customization of themes as per your preference with WordPress Customizer</li><li>Facility of adding a menu and animations to your mobile app</li><li>Automatic content updates</li><li>Push notification feature</li><li>Compatible on all major platforms &#8211; Android phone, iPhone, iPad and tablets</li><li>Mobile advertising and monetizing</li><li>Complete control over your app&#8217;s design and content</li><li>User-friendly</li><li>No technical knowledge required to create the app</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you download the Mobile App Canvas from MobiLoud, the team will take care of building the mobile app. Additionally, they will even maintain it. However, it&#8217;s not a free service. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/appful/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"appful (opens in a new tab)\">appful</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364817\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Being compatible with both: Android and iOS, appful is considered to be one of the best mobile app plugins to create a supreme mobile app. appful is created by SaaS company that assists companies, publishers and magazines to reach their target audience by creating enterprise software solutions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>appful provide features like:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Native social media sharing</li><li>offline reading</li><li>facility of &#8216;Read Later&#8217; and &#8216;Comments&#8217;</li><li>YouTube support</li><li>Live editing</li><li>Great app speed due to caching</li><li>Placing own advertisements in the app</li><li>Twitter profile page integration</li><li>Facility of using Google Analytics to inspect the mobile app traffic</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You are entitled with great mobile app designs at a fair price on appful which you can further customize them as per your preference. You will have to pay a nominal cost at the time of publishing your mobile app to the Apple App Store or Android Play Store. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>6) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/web2application/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Web2App (opens in a new tab)\">Web2App</a> </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364818\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This WordPress plugin easily converts your responsive website into a full native app. Even if the setup is quite easy, you will not have to compromise on the quality of the mobile app if it is created with Web2App. It is both, suitable as well as an affordable choice of the plugin that serves you with different customization facilities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the interesting mobile app features you can get with this plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>App rating to get customer reviews on Google Play</li><li>Startup splash screen</li><li>Different ways for mobile app&#8217;s display and navigation</li><li>Social sharing</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Above all, they also provide you with a video tutorial so that you are able to create your mobile app easily with this plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>7) <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wapppress-builds-android-app-for-website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"WappPress (opens in a new tab)\">WappPress</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-364819\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7.jpg 750w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>WappPress is considered to be the most cost-efficient platform while allowing you to convert WordPress website to Android app through simple click functionality. Here, you will not have to think of hiring the developers as even a non-developer can build the app with just a few settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Features of using WappPress include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Customizing features for templates and other pages</li><li>Multiple premade theme</li><li>Custom home page</li><li>Launcher icon</li><li>Custom splash screen</li><li>Push notifications</li><li>Google Play Store support</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have built your mobile app, you can simply publish it on Google&#8217;s Play Store on your own.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Which plugin will you choose?</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using any of these plugins to turn your WordPress site into a mobile app will carve your path towards reaching your target audience. Even if you have a responsive design, having a mobile app for your business will bring in more traffic, leads and ultimately sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, which plugin will you choose for your app? Are you aware of other plugins? Do tell us in the comments. </p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/7-top-plugins-to-turn-a-wordpress-site-into-a-mobile-app/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:25:\"https://oceanwp.org/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"